results.title: Prisoners of Doctor Doom! Part 1
results.description: Dr. Doom takes the Invisible Girl hostage.

results.title: Part 2 "Back to the Past!"
results.description: Dr. Doom brings the FF to his castle stronghold in the USA. There he sends the Torch, Thing and Mr. Fantastic back in time to retrieve the pirate Blackbeard's treasure.

results.title: Part 3 "On the Trail of Blackbeard"
results.description: The Thing takes command of a sailing ship in the era of the pirate Blackbeard

results.title: Part 4 Battle
results.description: The Thing takes on the role as Blackbeard the Pirate and wishes to remain in the past.

results.title: Part 5 "The Vengeance of Doctor Doom!"
results.description: Doom tries to kill the FF when they return from the past, but Invisible Girl saves them. Doom escapes with his jetpack.

results.title: The Startling Saga of the Silver Surfer
Klaw, the Murderous Master of Sound
Captives of the Deadly Duo! Part 1
results.description: Dr. Doom presents himself to Sub-Mariner

results.title: "When Super-Menaces Unite" Part 2
results.description: Dr. Doom gives a "Grabber" to Sub-Mariner and Human Torch discovers that Invisible Girl hides a photo of the Sub-Mariner in a book.

results.title: Part 3 "When Friends Fall Out!"
results.description: The Sub-Mariner plants the "Grabber" in the Baxter Building and it is lifted into space by Dr. Doom.

results.title: Part 4 "Trapped!"
results.description: The Baxter Building is set on a collision course with the Sun and the Sub-Mariner discovers that Doctor Doom has betrayed him.

results.title: Part 5 "The End... or the Beginning?"
results.description: Doctor Doom is flung out into space and the Baxter Building is returned to its foundation.

results.title: Prisoners of Kurrgo, Master of Planet X Part 1 "It Came From the Skies!"
results.description: Kurrgo sends a robot to take the Fantastic Four to Planet X.

results.title: Part 2 Outlawed
results.description: The robot from Planet X puts on a "hostility ray" to make people riot against the Fantastic Four.

results.title: Part 3 "Bound for Planet X!"
results.description: The robot grants the Fantastic Four asylum on Planet X.

results.title: Part 4 "Twenty Four Hours till Zero!"
results.description: Kurrgo orders the Fantastic Four to save his people from Planet X' destruction.

results.title: Part 5 "The End of Planet X!"
results.description: Kurrgo perishes on Planet X, but his people gets away from its destruction.

results.title: Prisoners of the Puppet Master!
results.description: The Puppet Master tests his radioactive clay that gives him the power to remote control people, that are modeled in the clay.

results.title: "The Hands of the Puppet Maker" Part 2
results.description: The Puppet Master gets the Thing under his command and imprisons the Invisible Girl. He then send the Thing and Alicia Masters to infiltrate the Baxter Building.

results.title: "The Lady and the Monster" Part 3
results.description: While acting under the Puppet Master's influence, the Thing is subjected to one of Mister Fantastic's potions that changes him back to Ben Grimm.

results.title: "Face-to-face with the Puppet Master" Part 4
results.description: The Puppet Master stages a jailbreak just to prove his might, Invisible Girl sends a distress signal to her teammates and the Puppet Master flees when meeting the combined forces of the Fantastic Four.

results.title: Death of a Puppet Part 5
results.description: The jail break is stopped by the Fantastic Four and the Puppet Master falls to what seems to be his death.
